{"word":"Shephatiah","slug":"shephatiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shephatiah</b> <a href=\"#/H8203\">H8203</a> <br/> 1. Son of David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=4'>2Sa 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=3'>1Ch 3:3</a><br/> 2. A Benjamite, father of Meshullam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=8'>1Ch 9:8</a><br/> 3. A valiant man who joined David at Ziklag<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=5'>1Ch 12:5</a><br/> 4. A ruler of Simeon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=16'>1Ch 27:16</a><br/> 5. Son of Jehoshaphat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=2'>2Ch 21:2</a><br/> 6. The name of two men, ancestors of families which returned to Jerusalem from captivity in Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=4'>Ezr 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=57'>Ezr 2:57</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=8'>Ezr 8:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=9'>Neh 7:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=59'>Neh 7:59</a><br/> 7. A descendant of Perez<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=4'>Neh 11:4</a><br/> 8. An enemy of Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=1'>Jer 38:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=4'>Jer 38:4</a>"}]}